/**
 * @description Returns {String} of HTTP path requests
 */
const MAIN_PATH = '/api/languages'

export default class Languages {
   static GET_LANGUAGES = MAIN_PATH + '/'
   static GET_LANGUAGE_BY_ID = MAIN_PATH + '/id/id='
   static GET_LANGUAGE_BY_NAME = MAIN_PATH + '/name/name='
   static CREATE_NEW_LANGUAGE = MAIN_PATH + '/'
   static UPDATE_LANGUAGE = MAIN_PATH + '/'
}
